<item>
            <title>[LU-15495] sanity test_71 ppc64le: dbench failed! linux-vdso64.so.1: No such file or directory</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15495</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8ab73e77-7af2-4ab0-b381-f166cd90cee6&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8ab73e77-7af2-4ab0-b381-f166cd90cee6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_71 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;copying /usr/share/dbench/client.txt to /mnt/lustre/d71.sanity/client.txt
copying necessary libs to /mnt/lustre/d71.sanity
tar: linux-vdso64.so.1: Cannot stat: No such file or directory
lib64/libpopt.so.0
lib64/libc.so.6
tar: Exiting with failure status due to previous errors
lib64/ld64.so.2
can&apos;t copy libs linux-vdso64.so.1
lib64/libpopt.so.0
lib64/libc.so.6
lib64/ld64.so.2 to /mnt/lustre/d71.sanity
 sanity test_71: @@@@@@ FAIL: dbench failed! 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This looks like a test script problem, maybe a test environment problem trying to install dbench?&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity test_71 - dbench failed!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
